This CD features a BBC soundboard recording of the Floyds performance of Atom Heart Mother at the Paris Theatre in London on July 16th, 1970 with a full choir and brass ensemble. Also Performed at the same location are track 1-4 ("Embryo", "Green is the Colour", "Careful With That Axe, Eugene" and "If") The material is taken from 2005 FM re-broadcasts and appears here in the best ever sound quality.
